# More info: https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/builder/#dockerignore-file
# Ignore everything by default and re-include only the files required for Go builds.
**

# Re-include Go source files (but exclude test files to avoid bloating images).
!**/*.go
**/*_test.go

# Re-include Go module metadata.
!go.mod
!go.sum

# Re-include configuration files.
!**/*.toml

# Allow Dockerfile targets that rely on git metadata (e.g. version stamping).
!.git
